data.description: PHENOMENAL property with over 9 acres of land!! Fencing and pasture for horses and other animals, in ground pool, 2 pool houses, tanning deck, outdoor fireplace,  3 gas log fireplaces inside, 80x30 workshop-3 garage bays. Portion of the shop is setup for the horse stable and tack room. Another portion of the workshop setup for a car garage/workshop. The workshop also has a large bar area, kitchen area and so much more!!!  Spacious master suite with fireplace and vaulted ceilings. Upstairs you'll find a large flex space with bunks, could use as a bedroom(it does have a closet) and two other rooms upstairs. Lots of storage! You will not want to miss out on this dream property!!
